santander consumer uk plc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Specialty Finance
Sub-Industry: Consumer Finance
Santander Consumer (UK) PLC, doing business as Santander Consumer Finance, provides financial services. The Company offers loans, leases, insurance, and other products for cars, motorcycles, caravans, and commercial vehicles. Santander Consumer Finance serves customers throughout the United Kingdom.




