HomeBusiness AreasHead Office Careers	
		


Head Office Careers





There are plenty of opportunities for motivated professionals at our Head Office. With a wide range of business and support positions available, if you’ve got the skills and experience to turn ideas into action  and the personal drive to develop your career, we have a role for you.
In addition to our Audit, Risk, Governance & Control functions, our key business support functions are:


Product Marketing, Brand and Customer Relationship Management

Product Marketing, Brand and Customer Relationship Management is responsible for products, marketing and brand communications for our UK businesses. They also conduct research, to help identify trends and understand how we can be closer to our customers.



Technology & Operations

Technology & Operations are responsible for all information technology, cost control and operations activity – including service centres and complaints handling.



Legal & Secretariat

Legal & Secretariat makes sure we comply with company legislation and regulation. It provides legal advisory services to the business, and manages subsidiary companies and their statutory requirements. 



Human Resources

Human Resources is responsible for delivering all people strategy and personnel support, including our learning function. They help our people reach their full potential, and ensure we’re retaining our talent.



Strategy & Planning

Strategy & Planning uses economic and market intelligence to generate consistent strategies, and develops initiatives to help us achieve our plans. 



Finance

Finance produces all financial information. That includes both internal management information, and external statutory & regulatory reporting. It also manages financial control and governance across our UK businesses. 

 Alison SimmonsHead of Financial Crime, Retail, Wealth and CET




Communications

Communications manages and promotes effective communication with our key stakeholders. These include our people, the media, the government, local communities and charities.



