Santander Consumer (UK) plc: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 1:54 PM ET
Consumer Finance

Company Overview of Santander Consumer (UK) plc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Santander Consumer (UK) plc, doing business as Santander Consumer Finance, provides vehicle loans in the United Kingdom. Its products include car, motorcycle, commercial vehicle, and caravan finances for private individuals, sole traders, and partnerships; and lease purchase, lease purchase with a balloon, and contract purchase facilities for business customers. The company also serves retail customers. It provides its services through a network of motor dealers and manufacturer partners. The company was founded in 1988 and is based in Redhill, United Kingdom. Santander Consumer (UK) plc operates as a subsidiary of Santander UK Group Holdings plc.


Santander House86 Station RoadRedhill,  RH1 1SRUnited KingdomFounded in 1988



Phone: 44 8000 851 759

www.santanderconsumer.co.uk







